summary: Adds a fast-travel map marker to the dock in Raven Rock and to the dock in Windhelm.
descriptionHtml:
DRAGONBORN DLC REQUIRED 

A simple mod that adds a fast-travel map marker to the dock in Raven Rock and to the dock in Windhelm in order to help further expedite a more lore-friendly and roleplay-friendly journey between Solstheim and Skyrim. 

Please enjoy. 

(This is my first ever mod. It\'s super simple, but I have aspirations for bigger and better mods down the road.)
author: Vikmourne
